/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="Meta 考虑云业务从人工智能能力中赚钱"&gt;今天的《Tech In Depth》&lt;/a&gt;杂志上报道称，微软和亚马逊本周宣布计划创建员工小组，帮助现场客户使用人工智能工具。她写道，“前沿部署的工程师”在十多年前就被 Palantir 所普及，并被 OpenAI 和 Anthropic 用来追求企业业务。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/tjnq4H1VNME_NkRPqdQGIfJ7ToXgNekwhcVpBs8zrBphNuZGwbYVwi4mMRhgnm0U8Kqcxkh1mKQdkVs37MzXw9q4Un2wyqxOvem_TG9MHLFQDZKw-3BkyilnJQdaw4c8Ky4X7UPvEr6frjagstKLiQUUhyTTiVDPOwWWp4Lily7cCs3gSWEttokre327A6jJhlMBhT8i4UrYHv2S56qWDovJUJI79ZQ47rgXlcU6watRvCxTsTo8xe-n1s5u_0OH9OnKKc2VG8HwXfhtOwpLAz4Y-P7x9nhmFaYeDpxpLo6uS4QLzaOFQn2SdCZ5g6pFOXTBdPH0rlmmcWitsx2HMHVBP8d1mKO995QeZfPSb0wC3nDhbarRRJIO56vtZMuGNqsIRwciCu5HCjHPcvZJegU_8CSSmqd6C7HgZOq6HGk5TrMHh0f02CqEc8AfGAKVZKWUieFKsNW3-ZnvZGPjRuHwk4fBiVpPvyt5--8pcA/DPWgGDCgZlcOCm5mfVm4APkt_VGkuEYC/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="技术深度"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;获取《Tech In Depth》时事通讯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;，了解彭博社世界各地记者对技术业务的分析和独家报道。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;本周问答&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;迪娜·巴斯 (Dina Bass) 在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/JZ7X4T0uZeI2BQdNW89t3BIejKcDZ8VeRThQqyWSrmFtQrNiBlKZZjrZpit6kV7P7apOrNJMk-tD1u12ed_GxWKNwR3jgmgN18z0vt5UzP4zGbbs90isMH0lmI6gHUoB01cYfYTGnfljkmBLOi-_Qv2UNLC8HUlyIti2pbeLnj9_RLYWGU_gf9vJcKebHsmRzxGHUYOpZocPBKM1mnhG4GhCRJ2PiXpcdaOxnGe5uU9YsWPi446PttvX26CP3_RCdyk1K4_R3pgWmTVUTWwQiRKq7lXoVLGcDPiuzlyt6V8mcrg3YnR8cpXs6Zlp2VEiNh4Nlxwyr6F44Dpmg_dN7VfyTLSuOlBBG-h45-MFJpZg4ok1hsoa2iig8qA_1sNsesI2Ns1d7Si_HDfOYy7EYwt15J_BRKZgACSdB2_0Zm6x_C-JniAz7QSxz095PxH6b1tURHx-i-fJ06GcYVnhpcYbbTb5FNR0rN0qRq-9QHheaNGXZATYKayRRLqyllsPIOZKu1xF9LvidrO43xZ8GoBsm7LuaZbEaGjAlbUiXeNVEeiZbk3XdTIs2A/