px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;就业数据低于彭博社调查中除一项预估之外的所有数据，这表明尽管近几个月出现强劲迹象，劳动力市场仍面临一些挑战。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;尽管面对伊朗战争的能源冲击，消费者支出&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/K-ci97Xj-h7MUZgMBemLSIw9N2FPvm4AOM8WvQ_RjbMzkTAOWWASTmRaSqz4uqMghnRVWt-uZCIWKbIRl4Arb1aPXewn8rdii6KUtUP2BwGUJkHI3v6UTQa-Ktwno1H1j2Kr39gzMVwv0nsk7VqhNGZ1HNCVGHuHuPKK9BwfqEPpISlKOeDED5I56SJW826HkiREuhBGGVNt422cSfkhf1Mtaanq2s2Iyj7sqPE61d8WWH4bmv9_OQfQUeRfvJj0amO8XJZlrK5TD79bzvTaRml-yF40jVKaNXAG178sJ9FXaD83_ioSUQi8sRhO4SQTzv7dMsX-AoLflJ00Jwtlzi8tHtOZ3aJrHZnOivcyyG2faEljRvp9nKYqokqSxphi-D7Lc6pU8CIl3SGZmnIIAoTgWH8W4fmwkxe9BmMglaphM_exoZYVTkTcHLIhaMvEW22Qn8d-OTmgzT-RsMocvyJBHq0DLr1ciMh8UAFv_EC5u3rz6Z5CToLCplyp1LG4ahYQW-yg4raV2oaXQ2s8/RMYX6_MLZFthe4Gb3T3DJietxEYUqBgS/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="通胀创三年新高 美国消费者支出回升"&gt;一直保持弹性&lt;/a&gt;，但美国人对高油价持悲观态度，这也可能使雇主对招聘持谨慎态度。此次回调是由于休闲和酒店业就业人数出现 2020 年以来最大降幅所致。 — &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dPpFnc5eEJnYmGSpXM3qF8Q0C_-7CPHbbc8BeoSn0JQ8r3okpKD2_XlWAtSCy4asLMse-Z2u5zjTCa0s3Z4rQSgItXPGF8PnXFOOfm5nbtJjrpdmwimq_wsgzpwymO6HvQFAYrXFuaHE6RQPe6XHD-cpcZ7g8wC5OYJayyMrhCFwo_M5vquUtOyk1tdtXfSiHQ89hKnvVqZRaoRqj8To8Yp4K220enD15Vlj8GQ2PQfH6tN8pZcnmdXYY8AEpFRAWlLBVRpxArevIhvy_4Zf2-wbU5uUx1wVlOlVIURgfONzY7iDcYiKN425-kameszNYXwIIHqzYvStoUzHXYaemKdWHEbXoPu7rOvA0Zsa0Jb6Kl1wKuaQyv4cKuoIlNF_hpI6o9fh8elx8bB-KoHZ-yj8joF8UUU-OBV_ERU9tOsd7SMkat-YLgaUObBAfrNwquavQrPaWSIUOGeY/WTxLxwjtGg_mydR7NBljGPZx3vQDWxTP/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="乔丹·埃尔布 |彭博社"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;Jordan Parker Erb&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;晚间简报将于 7 月 6 日星期一回归。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h3